TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Waiter: No he was just rather hot. We added him for a bit of spice.

Customer: Waiter, There is a sail boat race in my soup.

Hop on ya boat and join in on the fun!

 

 

Waiter, there's a lost cosmonaut in my soup

He's dismissed. Eat.

Waiter! Where's Walter?

Next to Waldo by the noodles

 

Waiter! There's a moderator in my soup!

Eat it before it destroys the megathread.

Waiter! Michael Scott is in my soup!

Waiter: It is Scottish soup and please don't call me Michael.

Customer: Waiter, there is Goldie Hawn in my soup.

Yes you orders ‘Murcia soup actress edition

Waiter! There’s a Donaudampfschifffahrtselektrizitätenhauptbetriebswerkbauunterbeamtengesellschaft In my soup!

I thought you wanted it Taumatawhakatangihangakoauauotamateaturipukakapikimaungahoronukupokaiwhen style?

Waiter! There is a probe in my soup!

Yes, it's there to sample the soup and bring the samples back to its homeplanet.

 

 

Waiter! The saucer my soup is on is flying!

Yes you got UFO soup

Waiter! There’s cereal in my soup.

Yes, this is Ceres.

Waiter! Some fresh Encelados?

Waiter: Sorry they are back in the very first post on this thread.

Customer: Waiter, there is a PotatoRoid in my soup.

Yes you ordered potatoes soup.

Waiter! There’s a BC ferry in my soup!

Edited July 27, 2021 by Stormpilot

Stop eating the seawater. Go to a diner.

Waiter! Why is that guy drinking water from the sea near the ship?

Edited July 27, 2021 by kerbiloid

He's from Vancouver and hes drunk why isnt he drinking sea water

Waiter! There is soup in my soup in my soup in my soup in my soup in my soup

Thats just leftovers from an old Libbys commercial

 

Waiter! Theres a Miller welding rig in my soup!

It's Miller's soup tank. Why did you  take it?

Waiter! Bill! Also Jeb and Bob.

You ordered spaghetti soup, kerbal spaghetti!

Waiter! There's a waiter in my soup!

Yes, he's waiting.

 

 

Waiter! There's a kerbal strapped inside a tin can atop a missile in my soup!

Spoiler

For all Kerbalkind, anyone?

yes, it's trying to heat both your soup and your temperament.
waiter, there's nothing in my soup! (as in, the bowl is completely empty)

Well, I was a bit hungry on the way to your table...

Waiter! There is a rickroll in my soup!

Waiter: I am sorry but he gave up on you.

Customer: Waiter, there is an obscure reference in my soup.

Hold on and let me get the clarification spoon for that.

 

Waiter there's an outta control old man in my soup

Ah yes you ordered the 1940s Finnish soldier who has to much meth (true story).

Waiter! There’s a MK82 bomb in my soup!

Waiter: There won't be in 5.4.3.2....................................................

Customer: Waiter, there is a mushroom cloud in my soup.
